Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,MASTER OF DARKNESS AGAINST HIS PUPIL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are all worthless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You are vermin to Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender will not be allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.69,0:02:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone from this world,\Nalong with this entire country!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make sure your final screams are loud\Nenough that King Ban can hear them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shadow Legion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Vermin?! Surrender won't be allowed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks humans are\Nthis world's garbage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does he think he is?! That does it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, run when you have the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful out there, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Uh, what about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will look after those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:03:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, calm down!\NYou won't beat him by losing your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! But he just makes me so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I'll show him that humans\Naren't as weak as he thinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were wounded rescuing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you immortal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Guy's surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go help them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I thought your Refractor Fist\Nonly works on living creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it work on those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,For enemies like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you use brute force!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. I won't be teasing her any time soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! You're up against me,\Nyou colossus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll blow your head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IORA!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There! That should open a hole in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It did, but not by much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And now a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Miasmas, take him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys cast magic impair spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Mahoton!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry and finish!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax yourself.\NYour agitation will affect the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Once this is complete, you will be able\Nto fight any enemy on equal ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me. Trust this sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And trust Jank's son and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm counting on you, Popp, Maam,\Nand everyone in Papunica!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be there soon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't beat us so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Miss Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way to gallantly help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Baduck, Papunica's greatest\NInventor Swordsman, am coming to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who in the world is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's too many.\NI'll have to take them all out with...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp, I heard you used Five Finger Flares.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Never use it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That spell is practically Forbidden Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a creature with no regard\Nfor its own life can use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll shorten a normal human's lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's for your friends,\Nbut if you keep that sort of thing up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentor! Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentor, you didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be long now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shortened as it is,\Na hundred years is still too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:07:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering how short Aban and Roka got.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Popp. You're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NIn time, you'll learn powerful spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you understand?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What an army!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop!\NShow an opening and they'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Help is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm. That one has spirit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry.\NIn time, you'll learn powerful spells.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In time is too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I need it now, Mentor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Finger Flares Bomb!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy cow! When did he learn that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to keep up! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Roar, {\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Vortex Axe!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody! Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IORA!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How's that?! I got them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah I'm fine. I'm just a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is the colossus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you think it was over, you fools?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Shadow Legion is an immortal force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So long as they have Dark Aura,\Nthey will continue to resurrect!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In Sovereign Rock Castle's right chest,\Nthe Lung Chamber,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}new Armoured Warriors\Nare constantly imbued with Dark Aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lung Chamber?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Sovereign Rock Castle\Nhad such a forbidden chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then their army...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...is infinite?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We... We might be done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You disappoint me, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're really a Disciple of Aban,\Ndon't whine over enemies like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just defeat them all! No matter\Nhow many times they're resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was getting too noisy\Nto focus on training.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to silence them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmph! What a show-off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Showing up at the perfect moment as usual!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another strange guy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe Miss Maam is\Nmore popular than I imagined.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem well, Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can reminisce\Nafter we defeat that behemoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see your overconfidence\Nhasn't changed, Hyunckel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out of there, Mystban!\NYou're going to be defeated by me anyways!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you save me the trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the power of my Shadow Legion,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the terror of\NDark King Ban's Sovereign Rock Castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the ultimate armour\Nof the Shadow Legion that Flazzard used!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go forth, Dead Armours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Three of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! By yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd only begun training!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The essence of the Aban Style\Nisn't about the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The basics of Earth, Sea, and Air,\Nonce mastered are easily applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Babysit Popp for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!\NAre you picking a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out! They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Earth Strike!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That first attack was Earth Strike,\Na powerful attack like Earth Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And this was Aban Style Spear Technique's\Nfastest attack, Wave Strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It hardly bears mentioning,\Nbut my strongest attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,remains just as powerful,\Neven with a different weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bloody Sukuraido!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He easily wiped out enemies\Nwe previously struggled against!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit. I hate to admit it,\Nbut he really is powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Grand Cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with the games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out or I blow away the castle's head\Nwith you in it, Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!\NI'm not letting you show off any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I said back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban taught Hyunckel\Nthe Dark Technique
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,back when he was in the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If Aban is his Master of Light,\NMystban is his Master of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a battle between\Nthe Master of Darkness and his pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For Hyunckel,\Nit's settling his own dark past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're finally ready\Nto fight me, Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.49,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BLOODY SUKURAIDO!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.49,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}TOMAKUGUTSOSHO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me make one thing clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pitiful attack\Nwouldn't scratch Sovereign Rock Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have chosen to reveal myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You betrayed the Dark Army,\Nand embarrassed me in front of King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to kill you by my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become quite the chatterbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when you trained me,\Nyou barely said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NI'll make you like you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I kill you, you'll be quiet forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not possible. Not with your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out that flurry of attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that?! What did he do?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Such hastily learned spear skills\Ncan't match my killing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,See if they're hastily learned\Nfor yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban Stye Spear Technique, {\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Wave Strike!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Byut Deathstringer!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His finger!\NRapidly stretching steel claws!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool. This attack can be done\Nwith any finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Tomakugutsosho!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As a skill of darkness,\NI never intended to use it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll make a fitting end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Die by the skill you taught me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now pierce yourself with your own hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My... My Dark Puppetry Aura Hand\Nis perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You've said yourself\Nthat it surpassed yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weaker than when you were\Nthe Undead Legion Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Having sided with justice,\Nyour Dark Aura is not what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your father never give you a toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:17:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happens to broken toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Maam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! That was too reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How did he...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it was more\Npointless than reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To sustain wounds\Nfor one as useless as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! An adept warrior\Nlike Hyunckel isn't useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He was only adept when he was\Na Dark Swordsman in the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's just a mongrel\Nwith some skills in Light and Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!\NI've never neglected my training!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned the Aban Style Spear Technique!\NI may have gotten stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wouldn't have become weaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:18:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is simple.\NYour Dark Aura has diminished in power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It once overflowed with hate for Aban.\NHate which I taught you to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But the great King Ban saw through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He saw the deeply buried feelings\Nyou had for Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deep down, you admired and\Nwere grateful for Aban's kindness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your single-minded obsession with revenge\Nmade you bury such feelings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a result, you possessed\Npolar opposite energies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your body contained both\Nthe Aura of Justice and the Dark Aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It made you the ultimate warrior.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A body wielding\Nthe powers of both good and evil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the secret\Nto your undying strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Having awakened to justice and using\NAura of Light attacks like Grand Cross,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,your power is only half what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot defeat my true Dark Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You lie! I won't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall dispose of my mistake myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't harm Hyunckel! I'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not just Maam!\NDon't forget we're here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you can't fight all of us at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish insects. You can't even see\Nyou're already caught in my web.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this spider web-like thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Dark Puppetry Aura Decimation Field!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tomakugutsosho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's caught everyone here at once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unbelievable! Is this the depths\Nof Mystban's Dark Aura?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's unbeatable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to resist him with my own\NDark Power to fight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who can move\Nwithin the Decimation Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do, Hyunckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,try to stop this flow of Aura\Nwith your own Dark Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let my wrath burn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let my hate and malice towards him boil!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The power... The Dark Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't move a finger\Nwith darkness like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hate... Hate him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just as I once hated Aban!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We might all die\Nif you don't regain your power of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't bear to see\Nthose ruthless eyes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to fight,\Nfight with only the power of good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've stopped resisting. So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can die together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Byut Deathstringer!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?! My Decimation Field?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost made\Nthe same foolish mistake again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I choose... the Light of Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:07.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:11.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:15.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:19.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:22.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:26.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:30.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:34.62,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:38.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:42.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
